v.query:
SELECT "CountrySynonyms"."Name" AS "Country_Name"
FROM "Country"
  INNER JOIN "CountrySynonyms" ON (("Country"."ID" = "CountrySynonyms"."ParentID") AND ("Country"."MapCode" = "CountrySynonyms"."MapCode"))
WHERE (("Country"."ISO3166_3" = _UNICODE_FSS 'AUS') AND ("CountrySynonyms"."IsDisplayName" = 1) AND (("CountrySynonyms"."Locale" IN (_UNICODE_FSS 'en_US')) OR ("CountrySynonyms"."Locale" IS NULL)))
GROUP BY 1

v.query-trunc:
SELECT TRY_CAST(SPLIT_PART("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG", '_', 1) AS INT) AS "QUERY_TAG - Split 1"
FROM "ACCOUNT_USAGE"."QUERY_HISTORY" "QUERY_HISTORY"
WHERE (("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" >= 1) AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" <= 7) AND STARTSWITH(LTRIM(LOWER("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG")),'96') AND (TRY_CAST(SPLIT_PART("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG", '_', 1) AS INT) IS NULL))
LIMIT 1

v.query:
SELECT TRY_CAST(SPLIT_PART("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG", '_', 1) AS INT) AS "QUERY_TAG - Split 1",
  (TRUNC((CASE WHEN 15 <> 0 THEN ((((EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM "QUERY_HISTORY"."START_TIME")-EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM "t0"."__measure__0"))/(60*60*24)) * 1440) * 60) / 15 END)) * 15) AS "Sample Time (round param) (copy)",
  COUNT(DISTINCT "QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER") AS "ctd:CLUSTER_NUMBER:ok"
FROM "ACCOUNT_USAGE"."QUERY_HISTORY" "QUERY_HISTORY"
  INNER JOIN (
  SELECT "QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG" AS "QUERY_TAG",
    MIN("QUERY_HISTORY"."START_TIME") AS "__measure__0"
  FROM "ACCOUNT_USAGE"."QUERY_HISTORY" "QUERY_HISTORY"
  WHERE (STARTSWITH(LTRIM(LOWER("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG")),'96') AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" >= 1) AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" <= 7))
  GROUP BY 1
) "t0" ON ("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG" IS NOT DISTINCT FROM "t0"."QUERY_TAG")
WHERE ((TRY_CAST(SPLIT_PART("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG", '_', 1) AS INT) <> 962) AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" >= 1) AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" <= 7) AND STARTSWITH(LTRIM(LOWER("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG")),'96'))
GROUP BY 1,
  2

FROM "ACCOUNT_USAGE"."QUERY_HISTORY" "QUERY_HISTORY"
WHERE (("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" >= 1) AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" <= 7) AND STARTSWITH(LTRIM(LOWER("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG")),'96') AND (TRY_CAST(SPLIT_PART("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG", '_', 1) AS INT) IS NULL))
LIMIT 1

SELECT TRY_CAST(SPLIT_PART("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG", '_', 1) AS INT) AS "QUERY_TAG - Split 1",
  (TRUNC((CASE WHEN 15 <> 0 THEN ((((EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM "QUERY_HISTORY"."START_TIME")-EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM "t0"."__measure__0"))/(60*60*24)) * 1440) * 60) / 15 END)) * 15) AS "Sample Time (round param) (copy)",
  COUNT(DISTINCT "QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER") AS "ctd:CLUSTER_NUMBER:ok"
FROM "ACCOUNT_USAGE"."QUERY_HISTORY" "QUERY_HISTORY"
  INNER JOIN (
  SELECT "QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG" AS "QUERY_TAG",
    MIN("QUERY_HISTORY"."START_TIME") AS "__measure__0"
  FROM "ACCOUNT_USAGE"."QUERY_HISTORY" "QUERY_HISTORY"
  WHERE (STARTSWITH(LTRIM(LOWER("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG")),'96') AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" >= 1) AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" <= 7))
  GROUP BY 1
) "t0" ON ("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG" IS NOT DISTINCT FROM "t0"."QUERY_TAG")
WHERE ((TRY_CAST(SPLIT_PART("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG", '_', 1) AS INT) <> 962) AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" >= 1) AND ("QUERY_HISTORY"."CLUSTER_NUMBER" <= 7) AND STARTSWITH(LTRIM(LOWER("QUERY_HISTORY"."QUERY_TAG")),'96'))
GROUP BY 1,
  2
